{"tid":2119224,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想讀精算嘅入一入嚟 你問有人答","createTime":"2020-07-22T03:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T19:38:31.000Z","uid":251834,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"86ea44c84aa3a1528d329007b2e5a4dfd63d29b9","tid":2119224,"uid":251834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">入精算 悔終身 IVE Found Dip 更稱心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n是咁的 相信都冇咩人首選係精算啦 不過都講下啦<br />\n<br />\n(1) 我好鍾意數學，讀精算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />精算唔係好「數學」嘅 鍾意數學嘅可以cuhk數學精研<br />\n不過唔係數底超好嘅咁精算<span class=\"x-small\">intern</span>又冇咁易乞食嘅<br />\n<br />\n(2) 神科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港得4111係真神科 精算一早唔係<br />\n<br />\n(3) 讀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nStat/Finance<br />\n<br />\n(4) QFin/(AC/IFAA)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nQFin應該易啲入ibank  精算應該易啲入insurance<br />\n<br />\n(5) 乞食？<br />\nintern好搶手<br />\n<br />\n(6) HKU/CU<br />\n不用分那麼細 內容應該差唔多 聽講HKU難啲<br />\n<br />\n(7) 讀嘅嘢難唔難?<br />\n所有course都有人A+ 有人C range<br />\n不過大學本來就唔應該太簡單<br />\n<br />\n(8) 夠分入medic/dental/poly 3寶<br />\n此post已完<br />\n<br />\n係咁多先 有人想問再答<br />\n讀緊/想讀精算嘅都可以傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2210d2de89f7bc91c1bad03d7ebd5dbda6bc1c8","tid":2119224,"uid":194304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb9f747169bffdc146c0bf18c977c898255f962","tid":2119224,"uid":347237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:57:52.000Z","msg":"精算真乞米科"},{"pid":"86face3f6e150fedb1724569cce69cffb53071d9","tid":2119224,"uid":147718,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:00:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n畢左業搵Perm 難撚到仆街<br />\n就算有工 放左工仲要係咁溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e935dc7e785f27661f6b20317b2e1a9c7a79bf6a","tid":2119224,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:01:28.000Z","msg":"歡迎入去分享下<br />\n等大家揀專科嘅時候諗一諗邊個專科會更岩自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[逆向思維] 講下自己熟悉嘅專科有咩人係唔岩讀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2119208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2119208</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"89397564ef6d62e9a106dfdc0335badf648f969d","tid":2119224,"uid":200266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入嚟比stat強姦"},{"pid":"3ff3534c2cfbff4d994c713f01570cb26a190472","tid":2119224,"uid":275506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"其實都係睇你考左幾多個試 讀精算唔等如入到行<br />\n<br />\n利申: 做緊"},{"pid":"e6c85fdcec778b61e18ee124faeece27937d9f90","tid":2119224,"uid":251834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89397564ef6d62e9a106dfdc0335badf648f969d","tid":2119224,"uid":200266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入嚟比stat強姦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"Year 1得一科真係STAT咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7bd054953a0ed45105aba657d67a9b5fda16f0","tid":2119224,"uid":200266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6c85fdcec778b61e18ee124faeece27937d9f90","tid":2119224,"uid":251834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89397564ef6d62e9a106dfdc0335badf648f969d","tid":2119224,"uid":200266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch